WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.220
So shitty news, or really shitty news?
要听坏消息 还是更坏的消息？

00:03.320 --> 00:05.460
A, the first one.
我选第一个

00:05.700 --> 00:07.300
There's a storm up there.
山上有暴风雪

00:07.420 --> 00:11.500
Well, thanks for the bulletin, Tom, we can't even see the goddamn thing.
哦 汤姆 谢谢你的好心相告 我们根本看不清外面

00:11.580 --> 00:14.020
They won't let us fly up until the weather clears.
他们不准我们飞上去 得等到转晴

00:14.140 --> 00:15.900
Well, when do they expect it to clear?
预计什么时候才能转晴？

00:16.000 --> 00:18.360
Uh, next spring, sometime.
呃 明年春天的某个时候吧

00:20.280 --> 00:23.280
That's the really shitty news, in case you were wondering.
这就是我刚才说的"更坏的消息"

00:31.500 --> 00:34.300
Well, maybe next time.
那就下次吧

00:34.300 --> 00:36.800
Yeah.
好

00:36.920 --> 00:39.520
Next spring.
明年春天…

00:40.620 --> 00:43.100
So now what?
现在怎么办？

00:43.260 --> 00:47.780
Well, maybe your mountain's trying to tell us something.
要我说 也许你的神山想表达一些讯息

00:47.780 --> 00:49.500
What do you mean?
什么意思？

00:49.820 --> 00:52.920
Maybe we've been gone long enough.
也许我们离开太久了

00:52.920 --> 00:56.360
Gone long enough? Gone long enough for whom?
离开太久了？谁离开太久了？

00:58.020 --> 01:00.400
Oh. No, I get it.
哦 我明白你意思了

01:00.480 --> 01:03.680
The mountain isn't telling us it's time for us to go home.
这山想说的 不是让我们回家

01:04.400 --> 01:09.120
The mountain is telling you to tell me it's time for me to go home, right?
而是想让你跟我说 让我回家 对吧？

01:09.240 --> 01:12.000
- Yeah. - You shit.
- 对 - 混账老东西

01:12.280 --> 01:15.640
Why don't you worry about your own, and let me worry about mine, okay?
各人自扫门前雪 休管他人瓦上霜 听见没？

01:15.640 --> 01:18.860
Okay, okay! You don't have to get chippy with me.
好吧 好吧 不用对我心焦气躁的

01:19.220 --> 01:22.640
- What's next? - Next, Hong Kong.
- 下一站是哪儿？- 下一站 香港

01:22.640 --> 01:24.640

